column1: Baby Barnaby's////My favorite was the banana pancakes and the green eggs!! I highly recommend the green eggs
column2: which are scrambled eggs with spinach
column3: artichoke hearts and cheese!! It was so creamy and delicious!! It came with toast
column4: chicken apple sausage and potatoes. The potatoes were bite size and super crispy! The banana pancakes were thick
column5: slightly crispy and moist on the inside. There were slices of bananas on the inside!! I also tried the chicken fried steak
column6: which was smothered in gravy. The gravy was great!! It had chunks of sausage in it. I also got the biscuits and gravy which was delicious as well. The biscuits were sweet and the gravy added the perfect amount of savory taste to the dish.
